                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2003-03-17</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Fascinating, thorough in its analysis, beautifully designed reader/player. Good, well-rounded selection of texts and new media objects with no attempt to be exhaustive (to the editors' credit). I plan to use it as one of the texts in an upcoming university course.</span>
                  
              
